里活有間大酒店扮冇荷過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970b44435d9f83adffa2111f400dc906cb3a9069","tid":51333,"uid":25569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:31:27.000Z","msg":"清侵摩佢教整叉燒包囉"},{"pid":"a8c18281dd26daf0c9006ebc874a484cd82030f5","tid":51333,"uid":9026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:52:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人細個成日喺新都會公園玩捉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小學日日放學同同學上去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0994315e0c50ae1ce43e3d30b8392c07cfde3f14","tid":51333,"uid":7004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:59:12.000Z","msg":"何一何二孖三孖四點到你唔憤氣get out you two"},{"pid":"5a723a8a4fbaaf96b05e21bbbaa381d2078887cc","tid":51333,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T20:15:19.000Z","msg":"有無人玩過隻叫 零入 既game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩法類似007但節奏快好多<br />\n我都唔明點解個陣咁快都跟到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可惜我地無傳去下一代 我臨小學畢業見啲細既已經玩緊第2樣類似忍者既game又係圍圈咁玩"}]}